          <div className="disclaimer-highlight">
            <p><strong>{isIDWActive ? 'üß† Smart Analysis Method:' : 'üì° Nearest Station Method:'}</strong></p>
            <ul>
              {isIDWActive ? (
                <>
                  <li><strong>Multi-station intelligence:</strong> Combines readings from several monitoring stations</li>
                  <li><strong>Distance-based calculation:</strong> Stations closer to you have more influence</li>
                  <li><strong>Real-time updates:</strong> Fresh data every 30 seconds</li>
                  <li><strong>GPS integration:</strong> Uses your precise location for accurate calculations</li>
